{{Han etym}}
An unorthodox variant {{Han simp|溫|f=𥁕|t=昷|nocap=y}} which can be found in various historical dictionaries. <!-- Refer http://dict.variants.moe.edu.tw/variants/rbt/word_attribute.rbt?quote_code=QTAyMjkwLTAwMQ#20 -->

Eventually adopted as an official form by the People's Republic of China in 1965 based on the {{w|Xin Zixing}} ({{w2|zh|新字形}}) standardized form of characters.
